。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　9 　　月　　9 　　日\r\n                                書記官  鄭蕉杏","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ULDV/110%2c%e9%87%8d%e8%a8%b4%2c44%2c20210909%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ULDV,110,重訴,44,20210909,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"重訴","JNO":"44","JDATE":"20210909","JTITLE":"土地所有權移轉登記等"}